aring \\\"large-scale\\\" destabilising acts during the upcoming Olympic Games in Paris.\", \"from\": 3866, \"to\": 4023, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3866, \"end\": 3879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.355558025891479e-38, \"text\": \"French police\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\"}, {\"begin\": 3908, \"end\": 3915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.8432426476043854, \"rank\": 0.17449385439524373, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 4017, \"end\": 4022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999988758645, \"rank\": 1.1242335359388935e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During a raid at his apartment on the right bank of the Seine on Sunday, officers found documents believed to be linked with Russia's special forces, which are a part of the security agency FSB.\", \"from\": 4025, \"to\": 4219, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4081, \"end\": 4086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999993338844833, \"rank\": 6.657281256501162e-07, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 4150, \"end\": 4156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999990115598276, \"rank\": 8.04706455506486e-07, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 4215, \"end\": 4218, \"title